  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220951394783\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220951394783\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">안녕하세요</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">저번달에 발렌타인데이였죠</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">발렌타인날에 환자분들이 주신 초코렛이랑 과자랑 빵이에요</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">발렌타인데이는 여자가 남자한테 주는 날인데</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">병원은 그런거없어&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">ㅎㅎㅎ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">마음이 이쁘신 환자분들 덕뿐에 웃는날도있습니다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/line_characters_in_love\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/636299638ed45fe1.png\" alt=\"line_characters_in_love-4\"></a>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" ali